<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">they become individuals who can criticize and be criticized by participating in group work effectively, and this increases their self-confidence in relation to communication</Data></Cell>
