<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Participants will be able to understand the communication between different disciplines and practices, bring together different areas and parts of design and have the ability to create interdisciplinary perspectives and different designs.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412921&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
