<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 240</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History, Culture and Society of Turkey through Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">gain ability to analyze cultural products and write about them criticially and clearly</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413039&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 240</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History, Culture and Society of Turkey through Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">enhance their critical thinking, argumentation, writing and presentation skills with the aid of inclass presentations and essay-based exams.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413039&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Ders sonunda öğrenciler, mikrobiyomun temel prensiplerini kavrayarak klinik ve farmasötik multidisipliner uygulamalarda mikrobiyom üzerine araştırma yapabilen ve öğrendikleri bilgiyi etkin bir şekilde kullanabilen sağlık profesyonelleri olarak mezun olacaklardır. Dersin temel öğrenim çıktıları şunlardır: Mikrobiyota ve konakçı arasındaki dinamik ilişkiyi kavrayarak, mikrobiyomun gelişim sürecini ve vücudun farklı bölgelerindeki dağılımını açıklayabilirler.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413038&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mikrobiyotanın ve mikrobiyota değişimlerinin insan metabolizması ve hastalıklar üzerindeki etkilerini analiz edebilirler.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413038&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mikrobiyomun klinik ve farmasötik uygulamalardaki önemini kavrayarak, mikrobiyom temelli tedavi yaklaşımlarını açıklayabilirler.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413038&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Mikrobiyom araştırmalarında kullanılan ileri teknolojileri anlayabilir ve ilgili bilimsel literatürü eleştirel bir bakış açısıyla analiz edebilirler.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413038&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Eczacılık, tıp, biyoteknoloji, halk sağlığı ve genetik gibi disiplinlerle ortak projelerde etkin bir şekilde rol alabilirler.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413038&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
