</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 036</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Neuroscience</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">• Understand the basic structure and function of the nervous system and the associated methods used.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413036&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 036</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Neuroscience</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">• Describe why understanding the nervous system is crucial for linking the molecular level to behavior and health as well as to developmental processes.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413036&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 036</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Neuroscience</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">• Describe how the nervous system functions in relation to different domains, such as sensory systems, emotions and memory.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=413036&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 036</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Neuroscience</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">• Describe the interactions between the nervous system and other bodily systems to understand the multidirectional relationships between these systems as well as their collective impact on behavior and health.</Data></Cell>
