<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course gives the ability to discover new things, solve problems, gain time management skills, obtain and submit data, read and write scientific articles, and conduct subject-specific scientific research.</Data></Cell>
