<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course For Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Writing Skill-At the end of this course, students will be able to
• comprehend the process of writing from the first stage to the final stage
• recognize and produce the style, features and formats typical of academic writing
• develop the appropriate range of vocabulary
• be familiar with typical contexts and topics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Evaluating Essay Types</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Complete IELTS Cambridge</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412865&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course For Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Reading Skill-At the end of this course, students will be able to
• read for/understand specific information, main ideas, gist and opinions
• Use pre-reading skills to activate schemata and predict content of advanced texts
• identify the common types of support in arguments, their relevance and irrelevance, common argument flaws, opposing points of views and refutations
• expand targeted vocabulary</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Discussion
Vocabulary Study</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Complete IELTS Cambridge</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412865&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Molecular Biology and Genetics (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6248</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course For Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Listening and Speaking Skill-At the end of this course, students will be able to
• listen for specific information, main ideas and opinions
• identify main ideas and important details
• distinguish more important ideas from less important ones
• learn to use strategies to listen actively
• learn strategies to take clear notes
• use their notes to organize their ideas
• respond to questions on familiar and unfamiliar topics and to speak at length</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pre-Listening Discussion
Vocabulary Study</Data></Cell>
