<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Wartime and Postwar Cinema: German Nationalist/ Italian Neorealism/ American Censorship and Blacklists
Film and social engineering (post-war U.S.)
Outside the system
Films: Leni Riefenstahl, Germany, The Triumph of the Will (1935)
Vittorio De Sica, Italy, The Bicycle Thieves (1948).
