<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course plan will vary from week to week depending on the project and directions of the instructor with whom the student is working on his/her graduation thesis.</Data></Cell>
